#. js-lingui-id: HP7per
#: src/pages/settings/applications/utils/getStandardApplicationDescription.ts
msgid ""
"The base data model every Twenty workspace runs on.\n"
"\n"
"#### What \"foundation\" means\n"
"\n"
"Every Twenty workspace starts with this set of objects. They define the shape of your CRM, including relationships, activity, and reporting. Everything else, including marketplace apps, AI agents, and custom objects, plugs into them.\n"
"\n"
"#### Included objects\n"
"- **People & Companies**: contact and account records\n"
"- **Opportunities**: your sales pipeline\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: activity and follow-ups\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: automation and reporting\n"
"\n"
"Remove this app and the rest of Twenty has nothing to hang off.\n"
"\n"
"#### Build your own app\n"
"\n"
"Extend Twenty with your own objects, fields, logic functions, or AI skills. Scaffold a new app in one command:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Then inside the folder:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"See the [Getting Started guide](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) for the full walkthrough, and [Building Apps](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) for the `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIs."
msgstr ""
"Den grundläggande datamodell som varje Twenty-arbetsyta bygger på.\n"
"\n"
"#### Vad \"grund\" betyder\n"
"\n"
"Varje Twenty-arbetsyta börjar med den här uppsättningen objekt. De definierar formen på ditt CRM, inklusive relationer, aktivitet och rapportering. Allt annat, inklusive appar från marknadsplatsen, AI-agenter och anpassade objekt, kopplas in i dem.\n"
"\n"
"#### Ingående objekt\n"
"- **Personer och företag**: kontakt- och kontoposter\n"
"- **Affärsmöjligheter**: din säljpipeline\n"
"- **Anteckningar och uppgifter**: aktivitet och uppföljningar\n"
"- **Arbetsflöden och instrumentpaneler**: automatisering och rapportering\n"
"\n"
"Tar du bort den här appen har resten av Twenty inget att bygga på.\n"
"\n"
"#### Bygg din egen app\n"
"\n"
"Utöka Twenty med egna objekt, fält, logikfunktioner eller AI-förmågor. Skapa en ny appstomme med ett enda kommando:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Gå sedan in i mappen:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Se guiden [Kom igång](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) för en komplett genomgång, och [Bygga appar](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) för `defineApplication` / `defineEntity`-API:erna."

